Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:09.23,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so this is the beach in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.82,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,With all these people here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:13.49,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,it's tempting to just mow them all down\N at once, isn't it, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:14.23,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:16.24,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean here's salty?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:17.66,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:18.91,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:22.53,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,The best thing about swimsuits\Nis that you can boldly show off more flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:24.45,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:25.53,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:28.09,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Shouta?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:30.04,Italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't where to look...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:33.84,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.09,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make me happy to hear at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:37.55,Main,Security,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:38.36,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:41.43,Main,Security,0000,0000,0000,,Could you come with me? \NYour swimsuit is too skimpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:42.55,Main-Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:44.50,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:19.48,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:21.87,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You brought a spare swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.58,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,It's my scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.99,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that works for your swimsuits, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:29.18,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we looked them up on the internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:29.99,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:32.83,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more envious of what's \Nfilling out that swimsuit though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:34.89,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:37.18,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right, let's go play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:38.94,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:41.43,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.56,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:45.47,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been very excited all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I'm not a big fan of the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:49.93,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.39,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,That's too honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:54.44,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's hot, you get sunburned,\N and sand is annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.22,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.67,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer the indoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:03:00.06,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you come with us today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.13,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:04.99,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't have much \Nelse to do this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.94,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,My manager asked me to look \Nafter Shouta-kun, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:11.28,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,so I figured going with \Neveryone would be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:13.27,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know what's going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:14.67,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,That tsundere thing, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.78,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:17.55,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:21.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:24.40,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's put on sunscreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.51,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What an inferior species,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:28.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,having skin that gets damaged if you \Ndon't coat yourselves in such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.41,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here I go, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:33.10,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Do anything weird and you're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:36.88,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Shouta, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:40.10,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,There. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:41.44,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:47.19,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:48.33,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.45,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Switch, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.87,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Shouta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.87,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.13,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Am I coating you right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.89,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a demon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.51,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:12.05,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to seduce me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:16.14,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Lucoa, why don't you \Njust try being a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:17.89,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.49,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Next is watermelon splitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.40,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.63,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Further right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:25.15,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you went too far. A little left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:27.68,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, now just go straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:35.68,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You obliterated every last trace of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.13,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.75,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I want to swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:44.76,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:47.00,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go too far out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:48.73,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.02,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:54.46,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right. \NHe is scary, that Leviathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:58.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,That one time I was nearly \Nkilled really was a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.02,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:02.35,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him from behind and mistook him \Nfor Rahab when calling out to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.25,Flashback,Lev,0000,0000,0000,,Why you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:06.77,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no, it's because no one can \Nhelp you if you start to drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:10.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you humans can't \Nbreathe under water, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What an inferior species.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:14.00,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You can, Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:17.78,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can. Swimming to my heart's \Ncontent feels really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.79,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Does she have gills or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.91,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru, let's race to there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:24.55,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi,\N please give us the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.46,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:30.16,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,On your marks,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.47,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.20,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:36.69,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I forgot to tell them to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.05,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.55,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, Lady Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.80,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,First!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.31,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You went overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.81,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:52.70,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's time for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.32,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.46,sign_8559_112_Beach,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.46,sign_8559_113_Beach_Hut,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Beach Hut
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.46,sign_8559_114_Food__Shaved_Ice,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Food\N Shaved Ice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.45,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.49,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:05.82,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Miss Kobayashi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:09.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:14.08,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I just noticed that old man \Nhasn't changed much since back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:16.98,sign_8871_120_Strawberry,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Strawberry\NMelon\NLemon\NBlue Hawaii
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:14.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:19.98,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. When I was still a kid, \NI came here with my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.01,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:27.22,Flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them! Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:27.98,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:32.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.21,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:37.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:42.08,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell me more about your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:43.13,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.38,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.59,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.71,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was a normal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.22,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I was raised normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:57.09,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,They had me go to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:07:00.73,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I left home to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:05.18,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Every now and then I talk to my parents \Non the phone to tell them how I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:09.19,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I haven't seen them in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:14.23,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's a normal human family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:15.24,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:20.24,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did Miss Kobayashi \Naccept a dragon like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:25.24,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why would someone born \Nand raised normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:26.89,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.25,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:33.34,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,the humans of this world \Ncould accept dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:38.48,Flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them! Humans are evil! Kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:40.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:45.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:48.77,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:55.94,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling listless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:07:59.88,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:01.45,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ride you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.97,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,This really is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:24.56,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, so I'm excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.56,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:36.94,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, aren't you homesick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.19,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:44.66,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel like seeing my parents \Nafter what we just talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:47.56,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Every now and then I would \Nlike to see my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.29,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:51.21,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.72,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's bugging you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:57.58,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about introducing \Nyou to my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.24,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.17,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm sure they'd kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:13.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds violent, but I guess that's \N common sense in your world, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.76,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:17.00,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,From my parent's point of view,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:21.45,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely the weird one,\Nnot common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.45,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:32.46,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Talking to Tohru about things like \Nthis is kind of heavy. And sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:37.47,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,It drives home the difference \Nbetween "understanding words"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.80,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,and "understanding each other".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:43.30,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me realize we've lived \Nin vastly different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:51.01,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe that's all the more reason I want \Nto cherish this time we have together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:56.27,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I think that means you've \Nbecome independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:57.77,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Independent?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:10:01.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You've developed your \Nown unique set of values.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.28,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You mean I've become an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.13,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.75,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:13.54,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Most people don't try to become adults, \Nthey just can't stay children any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:16.41,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you've hooked something, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:23.55,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.63,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:31.51,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:46.45,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:49.71,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I won them in a lottery \Nat the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:03.44,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:04.33,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.26,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,A real dragon is way better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.24,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, Lady Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:25.87,sign_16362_198_See__see__How_s_,,0000,0000,0000,,See, see! How's that, Miss Kobayashi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.87,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,Shee, shee! How'f thah, Mih Chofahashi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.99,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand anything you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.00,sign_16590_202_Episode_7,K,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 7
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.00,sign_16590_203_Summer_s_Staples,K,0000,0000,0000,,Summer's Staples! (The Fanservice Episode, Frankly)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.75,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What on Earth is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:43.21,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,The admission line for Comiket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:47.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So we're supposed to provide \Ncover for Takiya here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.96,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Not cover. Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently two of his sellers \Nsuddenly collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:53.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:55.57,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,With my power, it will be easy \Nto exterminate them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:56.22,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:59.73,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, was leaving \NKanna behind a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:02.74,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot here that \Ncan't be shown to children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.24,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Man, thanks, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.97,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lifesaver!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:11.55,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you quite a bit anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:14.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't ask Mr. Fafnir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.13,sign_17602_218_Water__Dragon__S,Poster,0000,0000,0000,,Water \NDragon\N Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.13,sign_17602_219_Bullet_Hell__Gam,Poster,0000,0000,0000,,Bullet Hell \NGames
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:17.26,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's participating as a circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.13,sign_17626_221_Curse__Anthology,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Curse \NAnthology
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:18.16,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:20.00,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Participating as a circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:25.84,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,A circle's a group of people like us, \Nwho sell things they made to other fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:29.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So why did Mr. Fafnir do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.60,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,I recommended all kinds \Nof anime and games to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.02,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,and at some point he started drawing his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.40,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally enjoying this world, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.82,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kobayashi-san,\Nif you could handle sales,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:42.40,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,and Tohru-chan, if you could \Nmanage the line please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:43.76,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:46.29,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:53.95,Main-Top,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As of this moment,\N the third day of Comic Market has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.50,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:05.51,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:09.44,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's just barely on the verge of running!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:14.48,sign_18936_238_MISSING,,0000,0000,0000,,Desires
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:13.32,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Something powerful is holding \Nback their selfish impulses!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.47,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.98,sign_19049_241_Water__Dragon__S,,0000,0000,0000,,Water \NDragon\N Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.23,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,The new one, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:16.98,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's 1,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.86,sign_17602_218_Water__Dragon__S,,0000,0000,0000,,Water \NDragon\N Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:18.85,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Here, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:21.18,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,The new one and the previous one, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.32,sign_19210_247_Water_Dragon_Shr,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Water Dragon Shrine {\c&H5F4D46&}WA-91\N {\c&H0A06C8&}End of Line
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:24.33,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The end of the line for \NWater Dragon Shrine starts here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:27.15,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, please group closer together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:35.71,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, for tens of thousands of \Nindividuals to be able take such
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.46,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,unified action without any \Nprior exercises or training...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:41.67,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Something powerful must be influencing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.22,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:43.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:46.32,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a cosplayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.70,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:50.61,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.93,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were a cosplayer from abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.43,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a real maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.30,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.84,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,You're in character.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:13:59.77,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.77,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.98,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:07.10,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, could I please \Ntake your picture later?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:08.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm real!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:15.37,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The end of line starts here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.66,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,What incredible heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:22.41,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I'm in a fire drake's stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.96,Main,Clerk,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.46,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it's this bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:28.79,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Comiket is not to be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:31.08,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Still,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:36.89,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,what in the world could be attracting this\Nmany people and keeping them all in check?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.59,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:40.17,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:42.24,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:43.42,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Time to switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:45.19,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.20,sign_21380_282_Summer_Homework_,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,Summer Homework, Science\N{\fs12}Please select one of the following.\N1) Sunflower Observation\N2) Bug Collecting\N3) Daily Weather\N4) Electric Circuits\NSunflower Observation: \NObserve the growth of a sunflower every day!\NBug Collecting: Catch bugs near convenience \Nstores, parks, or nearby plazas!\NPaste the bugs you've gathered!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:54.19,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Bug collecting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:05.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crunchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:07.05,sign_21682_292_Grasshopper__Moi,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,Grasshopper\NMoist
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:07.05,sign_21682_293_Butterfly__Flaky,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,Butterfly\NFlaky
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:07.05,sign_21682_294_Cicada__Crunchy,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,Cicada\NCrunchy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:07.05,sign_21682_296_Where_did_you_fi,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:07.05,sign_21682_297_MISSING_,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,Let's Stick the Bugs We Found Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:13.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I think it's around this area...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.85,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fafnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:19.29,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd stop by since I'm on my break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:25.25,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Say nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.23,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:29.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who looks dead, Mr. Fafnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:32.11,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's what it's \Nlike for first-timers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:34.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have a look at your book?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:35.90,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.50,sign_17626_221_Curse__Anthology,Book,0000,0000,0000,,Curse Anthology
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.48,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Curse Anthology{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.95,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Th-These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.28,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You've printed real, effective curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:47.95,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Even how to inflict them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:50.80,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You could curse someone to \Ndeath if you read this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.42,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.22,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Only 1,000 yen?! That's cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bargain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:57.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it's way too dangerous \Nto be selling that to others!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:05.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Still, there are a lot of cosplayers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:10.07,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of humans dressed \Nup like the races from my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:13.82,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,They're having fun pretending to be \Ncharacters from anime and manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:16.27,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're practically the same, too, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:18.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I am a proper maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:21.84,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at me, \NI'm your loyal sex slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.12,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:25.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.55,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:30.08,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The sahuagin, goblin, and witch over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:32.08,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wonder what they're from.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:33.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.43,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:37.42,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Those three are real non-humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.09,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:40.20,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.55,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the other world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:44.79,Main,Sahagin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:47.39,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. What are you doing here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.94,Main,Witch,0000,0000,0000,,I came to spread my wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:53.65,Main,Goblin,0000,0000,0000,,I normally live disguised as a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:57.66,Main,Goblin,0000,0000,0000,,but coming to events like this \Nlets me enjoy time in my real form.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.78,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:04.03,Main,Sahagin,0000,0000,0000,,Why not take the chance to \Nenjoy your real form, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:06.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.53,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:10.08,Main,Sahagin,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:10.84,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.34,Main,Witch,0000,0000,0000,,That damn monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.08,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:15.80,Main,Goblin,0000,0000,0000,,The one that could eat us all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:16.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:18.03,Main,Three,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.22,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.64,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Dragons must be doing some crazy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.22,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:23.94,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:27.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,When dragons get hungry, we \Nonly eat as much as necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,And in the end, this world\Nis the survival of the fittest, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:32.41,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're not denying it, just giving \Nsupplementary explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:33.84,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.03,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:37.06,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Your outfit's out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:39.04,Main-Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:38.89,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not read the participant guide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:40.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Miss Lucoa came, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.20,Main-Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.03,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,She never learns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:46.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I look closer, \Nthere's a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:48.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Beings in their original form, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.29,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That many?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:50.04,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:56.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Those with great presence have left records of \Ntheir stays in this world on different levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:18:00.63,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,like Mr. Fafnir and Miss Lucoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:14.19,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:23.99,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to return to my real form...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.49,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:36.64,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you keep it where \Nit won't cause trouble, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.28,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:46.88,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, can I take your picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:49.89,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:55.17,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, can I take one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:55.66,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:56.77,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:57.48,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:02.07,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, can I get your \Neyes over here please?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.66,Main-Top,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, too, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:05.33,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.50,Main-Top,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, too, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:06.95,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:11.36,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. I came like I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:12.62,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:14.62,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:18.09,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be honest, it's pretty rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.37,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,But I can hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:27.42,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it seems like everyone here is being \Ndrawn to this place by something powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:30.26,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:36.93,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:42.61,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's something that only exists \Nin this place in this moment right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:48.75,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,And I think everyone loves that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.50,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:03.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:04.63,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:06.28,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take your picture soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:08.13,Main,Participant,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:11.63,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Geh, there's another line forming?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:18.52,Main-Top,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As of now, Comic Market 90 is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:21.39,Main-Top,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you for participating, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:24.49,Main-Top,Announce,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll see you again in winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:28.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:33.63,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you. We managed fine \Nwithout you during the second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:37.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm sorry for ditching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:38.79,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:43.93,sold out,,0000,0000,0000,,We've Sold Out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:43.92,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Fafnir, how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.23,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Poorly, it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:51.06,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,So how was it? What'd you \Nthink of your first Comiket?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.45,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:01.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I reconfirmed my love for \Nyou, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:02.36,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:05.50,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi-dono! Tohru-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:06.82,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,You were a huge help today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.00,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.17,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd like to ask for your help \Nas staff again this winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:13.65,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:18.17,Main,Sahagin,0000,0000,0000,,What will we print for our next thin book?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:20.84,Main,Goblin,0000,0000,0000,,How about a dragon maid girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.17,Main,Witch,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:27.63,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Free studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:30.90,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,My summer homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:32.52,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:36.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think you should \Nstudy something that you find
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:39.86,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,mysterious or would like to know more about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:41.76,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.53,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:49.52,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Studying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:51.43,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:27.97,sign_33686_435_Next_Episode,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,189)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:29.88,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi-san, there's a lot of \Ntalk about Tohru-chan on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:30.71,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.71,0:23:32.72,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,They mentioned you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.68,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,They said there was a sales lady \Nwith dead-fish eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:35.66,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:37.13,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,And they got turned on by those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:39.97,sign_33950_442_Episode_8,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(276,1)}Episode 8
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:39.97,sign_33950_443_New_Dragon__Elma,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(276,1)}New Dragon, Elma! (She's Finally Appearing, Huh?)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.13,0:23:38.22,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt a chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:40.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
